OL,3,CSex offence anonymity law ruled
OL,4,C'incompatible with press freedom'
OL,6,FA new law in Northern Ireland granting
OL,7,Fanonymity to sex offence suspects is
OL,8,Fincompatible with press rights to
OL,9,Ffreedom of expression, a High Court
OL,10,Fjudge has ruled.
OL,12,FMr Justice Humphreys declared it was
OL,13,Fbeyond Stormont's legislative
OL,14,Fcompetence to introduce the
OL,15,Fcontroversial Act which has the
OL,16,F"chilling effect" of imposing a
OL,17,Fcriminal sanction on public interest
OL,18,Fjournalism.
