OL,6,FAlthough Sir John recommended a
OL,7,Fprohibition on identifying those under
OL,8,Finvestigation for sexual crimes prior
OL,9,Fto being charged, his report did not
OL,10,Fsuggest extending anonymity beyond
OL,11,Ftheir deaths.
OL,13,FConcerns have been expressed that the
OL,14,Fnew law could prevent the exposure of
OL,15,Fnotorious offenders and risks
OL,16,Fsilencing victims.
