OL,6,FThe Irish News and Mediahuis, which
OL,7,Fpublishes the Belfast Telegraph,
OL,8,FSunday Life, Sunday World, Sunday
OL,9,FIndependent and the Irish Independent,
OL,10,Fjoined forces in a bid to have
OL,11,Fsections of the Act declared legally
OL,12,Finvalid. to seek a judicial review
OL,13,Fagainst Stormont's Department of
OL,14,FJustice.
OL,16,FA separate challenge to the lifetime
OL,17,Fanonymity clause was also taken on
OL,18,Fbehalf of the BBC, Times Media Ltd,
OL,19,FGuardian News and Media Ltd and other
OL,20,FLondon-based organisations.
