OL,6,FHe insisted the Act provides legal
OL,7,Fcertainty and a "temporal limitation"
OL,8,Fon prohibitions which could still be
OL,9,Flifted on request to a magistrate.
OL,11,FThe court also heard that only the
OL,12,FChief Constable or the suspect
OL,13,Fthemselves can seek to have the
OL,14,Fanonymity clause lifted during their
OL,15,Flifetime.
