OL,6,F"Interference with the Article 10
OL,7,Frights of journalists in this fashion
OL,8,Fcan only serve to restrict the
OL,9,Fcarrying out of important public
OL,10,Finterest investigations," he said.
OL,12,F"Restrictions on the exercise of
OL,13,Ffreedom of expression in this context
OL,14,Fmust be strictly construed and the
OL,15,Frationale convincingly established.
OL,17,F"The failure to recognise the category
OL,18,Fof case where public interest
OL,19,Fjournalism is concerned means that a
OL,20,Ffair balance between competing rights
OL,21,Fhas not been struck."
