OL,6,FDeclaring that the relevant sections
OL,7,Fof the Act are unlawful, he added:
OL,8,F"They are outside the legislative
OL,9,Fcompetence of the Northern Ireland
OL,10,FAssembly as they are incompatible with
OL,11,Fthe Article 10 ECHR rights of the
OL,12,Fapplicants."
OL,14,FIn concluding comments, Mr Justice
OL,15,FHumphreys stated: "Public interest
OL,16,Fjournalism serves a vital role in any
OL,17,Fdemocratic society.
